title: Live Regret Free | Gina Hatzis
description: Today we have an award-winning global speaker of 25 years and the founder of the Too Much Woman Movement, Gina Hatzis. Today, Gina shares techniques she teaches hundreds of 1000s of women to best achieve the confidence and self-trust we all need to create true magnetism.
